## What Changed

### Architecture Switch
We replaced Streamlit with `dash` and `dash-bootstrap-components` to achieve granular control over styling and layout logic without leaving Python.
- **[app_dash.py](file:///Users/pranavparthasarathy/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/fitness-tracker/app_dash.py)**: The new entry point. Configures standard Boostrap Darkly theme.
- **[assets/style.css](file:///Users/pranavparthasarathy/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/fitness-tracker/assets/style.css)**: Dash automatically serves CSS from the `assets` folder. We built a gorgeous CSS file focusing on glassmorphic elements, modern gradients, and hover transitions.

