## How to Run

Stop any existing Streamlit logs, then run:

```bash
python app_dash.py
```

The app will instantly be available locally at `http://127.0.0.1:8050`.

> [!TIP]
> This pipeline structure perfectly mimics industry data science dashboards. You now have the full control to tweak the HTML layout structure, add complex chart interactions, and style everything preciselyâ€”something that is notoriously difficult in base Streamlit!
